  <AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
    <defName>LBD_Miraboreasu_Childhood</defName>
    <slot>Childhood</slot>
    <title>禁忌巨兽</title>
    <titleShort>巨兽</titleShort>
    <description>作为不详的毁灭象征，黑龙的诞生和其他古龙种一样笼罩在迷雾中，人们对这种超脱于生态系统的巨兽知之甚少，其名字已经成为命运之战的象征。黑龙对自身以外的事物都极度蔑视，不认同任何存在。</description>
    <skillGains>
      <Social>4</Social>
      <Intellectual>4</Intellectual>
    </skillGains>
    <!-- <workDisables>ManualDumb,Cooking,Mining</workDisables> -->
    <requiredWorkTags>Violent</requiredWorkTags>
    <spawnCategories>
      <li>LBD_Miraboreasu_Backstory_Categories</li>
    </spawnCategories>
    <bodyTypeGlobal>Thin</bodyTypeGlobal>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Thin</bodyTypeFemale>
    <bodyTypeMale>Thin</bodyTypeMale>
    <forcedTraitsChance>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="2">Nerves</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
    </forcedTraitsChance>
    <passions>
      <Intellectual>2</Intellectual>
    </passions>
    <shuffleable>false</shuffleable>
  </AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
  <AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
    <defName>LBD_Miraboreasu_Adulthood</defName>
    <slot>Adulthood</slot>
    <title>毁灭之兆</title>
    <titleShort>毁灭之兆</titleShort>
    <description>传说中，曾经君临于世界的繁荣大国修雷德国，其王都在一夜之间被黑龙毁灭，曾经夸耀荣华的宫殿被付之一炬，以古城为中心的旧王都化为无法感受任何生命气息的不毛之地。黑龙将焚尽后的修雷德城堡作为自己的巢穴，这一带都被视为无法踏足的禁区，直到四位天尊骑乘翼龙飞临此地······</description>
    <skillGains>
      <Shooting>4</Shooting>
      <Intellectual>5</Intellectual>
      <Social>3</Social>
      <Crafting>5</Crafting>
      <Artistic>3</Artistic>
    </skillGains>
    <!-- <workDisables>ManualDumb,Cooking,Mining</workDisables> -->
    <requiredWorkTags>Violent</requiredWorkTags>
    <spawnCategories>
      <li>LBD_Miraboreasu_Backstory_Categories</li>
    </spawnCategories>
    <bodyTypeGlobal>Thin</bodyTypeGlobal>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Thin</bodyTypeFemale>
    <bodyTypeMale>Thin</bodyTypeMale>
    <forcedTraitsChance>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">FastLearner</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
    </forcedTraitsChance>
    <passions>
      <Shooting>2</Shooting>
      <Crafting>1</Crafting>
    </passions>
    <shuffleable>false</shuffleable>
  </AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
